Name: Ammo: Flamethrower Ammunition
Description: This is Ammunition for the flamethrowers.

Name: Ammo: Bullets
Description: Can be used with rifles, pistols and the like.

Name: Ammo: Energy Weapon Ammo
Description: Can be used with any weapon that fires energy beams, such as the blaster.

Name: Ammo: Shotgun Shells
Description: These are shells containing a carbon substance which will be released as pellets or a single slug, depending on the type of shotgun used.

Name: Augmented Nano Armor Sleeves
Description: The Nano Armor is designed by and for Nano Technicians. It is very lightweight, as it relies on nanobots to provide most of the protection. The armor is plugged directly into the user's nervous system, and uses it for information-gathering and data transfer. The armor can gather data in other ways - but without the information from the nervous system of the user, it works much less efficiently. Thus, high psychic ability and intelligence are required to use Nano Armor.

Name: High-Quality Cyber Armor Sleeves
Description: The Cyber Armor is lightweight, made with the Homo Nano in mind. It is built as an exoskeleton and pretty much carries its own weight, which makes it comfortable to move in. Also, the protection it provides depends on nanobots and sensors, connected to the nervous system of the user for highest possible data transfer rate. The higher quality versions of the Cyber Armor can also gather and use information directly from the user's Senses. High psychic ability is needed to keep the suit operational, and high intelligence is required to be able to actually utilize its functions.

Name: Flawless Energized Armor Sleeves
Description: The function of the Energized Armor is based on advanced physics. It is charged with negative energy that absorbs much of the charge from high-energy, low-wavelength sources like radiation and energy weapons. It also reduces the impact of attacks with high kinetic energy, such as projectiles and melee weapons.

Name: Flawless Kevlar Armor Sleeves
Description: The Kevlar Armor has been used for thousands of years, with only small modifications. It still counts among the best when you compare protection to weight. This version gives protection against most types of melee, projectile and energy attacks, and some protection against cold and chemicals.

Name: Augmented Martial Artist Suit Sleeves
Description: The Martial Artist suit is specially designed to fit the needs of a Martial Artist. It is a cloth suit, where every seventh thread has been replaced with a thread of lightweight, but very strong flexible metal. Numerous sheets of Kevlar are sewn into the suit in strategic places. The metal threads work as a conductor for most energy-based attacks, greatly reducing their impact. In combination with the Kevlar plates, the metal threads give excellent protection against melee and projectile weapons.

Name: Assault-Issue Omni-Pol Armor Sleeves
Description: This is the armor worn by the Omni-Tek police. It is a heavily upgraded version of the Metaplast Armor, and suitable for most normal combat situations.

Name: Assault-Issue Omni-Pol Elite Armor Sleeves
Description: This is the armor worn by the Omni-Tek elite police. It is a heavily upgraded version of the Metaplast Armor, and suitable for more extreme combat situations than the regular Omni-Pol armor.

Name: Assault-Issue Omni-Pol Forest Armor Sleeves
Description: This is the armor worn by Omni-Tek police on assignment in forested terrain. It is a heavily upgraded version of the Metaplast Armor, and suitable for most normal combat situations.

Name: Flawless Heated Plasteel Armor Sleeves
Description: The Plasteel Armor is usually found in two forms: the heated and the chilled version. Both versions give good protection against melee, projectile and energy weapons. The heated version is specially treated to shield the user from fire damage.

Name: High-Quality Steel-Ribbed Armor Sleeves
Description: The Steel-Ribbed Armor is one of the very few armor types that insulate the wearer against energy attacks. Instead of absorbing the energy, it actually prevents most of the energy from getting through. Beneath the layer of insulation you have a layer of steel ribs that will protect you against most melee and projectile attacks. The construction is very flexible, and a person with high Sense and Agility is able to wear this armor with great ease.

Name: Augmented Tech Armor Sleeves
Description: The Tech Armor is equipped with multiple sensors that detect virtually any type of attack, and cause the armor to perform the best possible counter-measures. In previous versions the user was able to select the settings he wanted, however certain breeds kept screwing up their settings more often than not. This option has now been disabled, and you can only use the factory default. The armor itself is quite heavy and uncomfortable, and requires a good amount of strength and agility if you want to use it for longer periods.
